      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is the ideal choice for a driver who values both aesthetics and mechanical integrity. The exterior maintains a deep, reflective shine, showing only the light, honest character marks of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the upholstery is supple and free of significant wear, while all electronic features\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, backed by a comprehensive service history that reflects proactive maintenance. It delivers a firm, responsive ride that inspires confidence on every commute. This is a complete, turn-key package for someone seeking a reliable and sophisticated daily driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
